Uses of Interface
adept.common.IType

  • Packages that use IType 
    Package Description
    adept.common
    Provides common data structures for use in the ADEPT framework, including the input Document and its TokenStream containing every Token, and the output HltContentContainer containing multiple kinds of annotations, such as EntityMention and Relation, which are based on the Chunk class.

    • Uses of IType in adept.common

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  OntType
      The Class OntType, which represents one concept from an ontology, where the ontology formally represents knowledge as a set of concepts within a domain using a shared vocabulary.
